<title>HONG KONG: Bear Stearns sets HK Telecom warrants.</title>
<headline>Bear Stearns sets HK Telecom warrants.</headline>
<dateline>HONG KONG 1997-05-08</dateline>
<text>
<p>The Bear Stearns Companies Inc said on Thursday it issued 230 million American style call warrants on shares of Hong Kong Telecommunications Ltd.</p>
<p>Ten warrants control one share.</p>
<p> STRIKE PRICE    HK$14.155   PREMIUM	    9.90 PCT</p>
<p> ISSUE PRICE     HK$0.222    GEARING	    6.71X</p>
<p> EXPIRATION	09.MAR.98   MIN EXER LOT     4,000</p>
<p> SPOT REFERENCE  HK$14.90    SETTLEMENT DATE  26.MAY.97</p>
<p> LISTING	   HONG KONG   LISTING DATE     28.MAY.97</p>
<p> NOTE		WITH ISSUER'S CASH OPTION</p>
<p>-- Hong Kong Newsroom (852) 2843 6370</p>
